Subject: [PATCH 2/3] feat(quiz): hint-on-incorrect, explanation-on-correct

- exercise tasks get an optional teacher-authored hint that points back
  at the material without revealing the answer
- grading now reveals the explanation only on a CORRECT answer; a wrong
  answer gets the hint instead, so retries stay a learning exercise
  rather than copy-the-feedback
- editor: hint field per question; clarified explanation label
- PUT whitelist allows the new field; sanitization keeps it server-side
